      <h1 class='title'>Administration of Estates Act (Northern Ireland) 1955 (c. 24 ( N.I.))</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='grand-committee-report-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c266GC</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_266gc' title='Col. 266GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c266GC' name='column_266gc' href='#column_266gc' rel='bookmark'>266GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03559'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_167' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        9 (1) Amend section 6A (spouse dying within 28 days of intestate) as follows.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03560'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_168' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (2) After "spouse" (in each place) insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03561'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_169' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (3) In the sidenote to section 6A, after "Spouse" insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03562'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_170' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        10 (1) Amend section 7 (rights of surviving spouse) as follows.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03563'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_171' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (2) After "spouse" (in each place) insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03564'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_172' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (3) In subsection (7), after "husband" insert ", or of section (Effect of separation order) of the <a href="/acts/civil-partnership-act-2004">Civil Partnership Act 2004</a>".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03565'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_173' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (4) In the sidenote to section 7, after "spouse" insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03566'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_174' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        11 In section 8 (rights of issue), after "spouse" insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03567'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_175' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        12 In section 9 (rights of parents), after "spouse" insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03568'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_176' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        13 In section 10 (rights of brothers and sisters and their issue), after "spouse" (in both places) insert "or civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03569'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_177' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        14 In section 11 (rights of next-of-kin), in subsection (1) after "neither spouse" insert "nor civil partner".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-03570'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_178' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        15 In section 38 (power to appoint trustees of infant's property), in subsection (5) after "marries" insert ", or forms a civil partnership,".
      </p>
      <ol class='xoxo'>
        
